    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Clay roofing tile, approximately semicylindrical in shape; laid in cornices with the units having their convex sides alternately up and down.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
